#: how-tos.php:14
msgid "Mandrill: How to tell WordPress to use wpMandrill."
msgstr "Mandrill: Sut i ddweud wrth WordPress i ddefnyddio wpMandrill."

#: how-tos.php:17
msgid "Mandrill: How to send a regular email."
msgstr "Mandrill: Sut i anfon e-bost rheolaidd."

#: how-tos.php:20
msgid "Mandrill: How to modify a certain email using the <em>mandrill_payload</em> WordPress filter."
msgstr "Mandrill: Sut i addasu e-bost penodol gan ddefnyddio hidlydd WordPress <em>mandrill_payload</em>."

#: how-tos.php:23
msgid "Mandrill: How to tell WordPress to change line feeds by BR tags in a certain email using the <em>mandrill_nl2br</em> WordPress filter."
msgstr "Mandrill: Sut i ddweud wrth WordPress i newid toriadau llinell gyda thagiau BR mewn e-bost penodol gan ddefnyddio hidlydd WordPress <em>mandrill_nl2br</em>."

#: how-tos.php:26
msgid "Mandrill: How to send emails from within your plugins."
msgstr "Mandrill: Sut i anfon e-byst o fewn eich ategion."

#: how-tos.php:29
msgid "Mandrill: How to use multiple editable regions in your template."
msgstr "Mandrill: Sut i ddefnyddio rhanbarthau golygadwy lluosog yn eich templed."

#: how-tos.php:54
msgid "Just by setting it up, all the emails sent from your WordPress installation will be sent using the power of Mandrill."
msgstr "Dim ond trwy ei osod, bydd yr holl e-byst a anfonir o'ch gosodiad WordPress yn cael eu hanfon gan ddefnyddio grym Mandrill."

#: how-tos.php:55
msgid "If you want further customization, you can use the <strong>mandrill_payload</strong> filter we've provided."
msgstr "Os ydych am addasu pellach, gallwch ddefnyddio'r hidlydd <strong>mandrill_payload</strong> rydym wedi'i ddarparu."

#: how-tos.php:56
msgid "And if you want an even greater integration between your application and Mandrill, we've created a convenient call to send emails from within your plugins."
msgstr "Ac os ydych am integreiddiad hyd yn oed yn fwy rhwng eich cais a Mandrill, rydym wedi creu galwad hwylus i anfon e-byst o fewn eich ategion."

#: how-tos.php:58
msgid "You can learn more about all of these features right from this page."
msgstr "Gallwch ddysgu mwy am yr holl nodweddion hyn o'r dudalen hon."

#: how-tos.php:65
msgid "Simply install wpMandrill and configure it to make it handle all the email functions of your WordPress installation."
msgstr "Gosodwch wpMandrill a'i ffurfweddu i drin holl swyddogaethau e-bost eich gosodiad WordPress."

#: how-tos.php:66
msgid "Once it has been properly configured, it will replace the regular WordPress emailing processes, so it's basically transparent for you and for WordPress."
msgstr "Unwaith y mae wedi'i ffurfweddu'n iawn, bydd yn disodli prosesau e-bostio rheolaidd WordPress, felly mae'n dryloyw i chi ac i WordPress yn y bôn."

#: how-tos.php:67
msgid "To test wpMandrill, log out, and try to use the <em>Forgot your password?</em> feature in WordPress (you don't need to reset your password though. Just check the headers of the email that it sends you, and you'll see that it comes from Mandrill's servers)."
msgstr "I brofi wpMandrill, allgofnodwch, a cheisiwch ddefnyddio'r nodwedd <em>Wedi anghofio'ch cyfrinair?</em> yn WordPress (nid oes angen i chi ailosod eich cyfrinair serch hynny. Gwiriwch benawdau'r e-bost mae'n ei anfon atoch, a byddwch yn gweld ei fod yn dod o weinyddion Mandrill)."

#: how-tos.php:75
msgid "If you're a Plugin Developer, and you need to send a regular email using wpMandrill, you don't need to learn anything else. You can use the good ol' <strong>wp_mail</strong> function, as you would normally do if you were not using this plugin."
msgstr "Os ydych yn Ddatblygwr Ategion, ac angen anfon e-bost rheolaidd gan ddefnyddio wpMandrill, nid oes angen i chi ddysgu unrhyw beth arall. Gallwch ddefnyddio'r hen ffyddlon <strong>wp_mail</strong>, fel y byddech yn ei wneud fel arfer pe na baech yn defnyddio'r ategyn hwn."

#: how-tos.php:76
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "Er enghraifft:"

#: how-tos.php:77
msgid "&lt;?php wp_mail('your@address.com', 'Your subject', 'Your message'); ?&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;?php wp_mail('your@address.com', 'Your subject', 'Your message'); ?&gt;"

#: how-tos.php:85
msgid "By default, wpMandrill uses only one editable section of your templates: <em>main</em> so its use is transparent for the you."
msgstr "Yn ddiofyn, mae wpMandrill yn defnyddio dim ond un adran olygadwy o'ch templedi: <em>main</em> felly mae ei ddefnydd yn dryloyw i chi."

#: how-tos.php:86
msgid "If you need to use more than one, <em>main</em> included, you need to provided an array with the content to use for each editable region involved. This array should be supply in the field \"html\" of the payload."
msgstr "Os oes angen i chi ddefnyddio mwy nag un, gan gynnwys <em>main</em>, mae angen i chi ddarparu arae gyda'r cynnwys i'w ddefnyddio ar gyfer pob rhanbarth golygadwy dan sylw. Dylid darparu'r arae hwn ym maes \"html\" y llwyth."

#: how-tos.php:87
msgid "This array has the same structure of the parameter <em>template_content</em> of the API call <a href=\"https://mandrillapp.com/api/docs/messages.html#method=send-template\" target=\"_blank\">send-template</a>:"
msgstr "Mae gan yr arae hwn yr un strwythur â pharamedr <em>template_content</em> y galwad API <a href=\"https://mandrillapp.com/api/docs/messages.html#method=send-template\" target=\"_blank\">send-template</a>:"

#: how-tos.php:88
msgid "$message[\"html\"] = array( array(\"name\" => region_name_1\", \"content\" => \"My awesome content for Region 1\"), ... , array( \"name\" => region_name_2\", \"content\" => \"My awesome content for Region 2\") )"
msgstr "$message[\"html\"] = array( array(\"name\" => region_name_1\", \"content\" => \"My awesome content for Region 1\"), ... , array( \"name\" => region_name_2\", \"content\" => \"My awesome content for Region 2\") )"

#: how-tos.php:95
msgid "if you need to fine tune one or some of the emails sent through your WordPress installation, you will need to use the <em>mandrill_payload</em> filter."
msgstr "os oes angen i chi fân-diwnio un neu rai o'r e-byst a anfonir trwy eich gosodiad WordPress, bydd angen i chi ddefnyddio'r hidlydd <em>mandrill_payload</em>."

#: how-tos.php:96
msgid "To use it, you must create a function that analyzes the payload that is about to be sent to Mandrill, and modify it based on your requirements. Then you'll need to add this function as the callback of the mentioned filter, using the <em>add_filter</em> WordPress call. And finally, insert it into your theme's functions.php file or you own plugin's file."
msgstr "I'w ddefnyddio, rhaid i chi greu ffwythiant sy'n dadansoddi'r llwyth sydd ar fin cael ei anfon i Mandrill, a'i addasu yn seiliedig ar eich gofynion. Yna bydd angen i chi ychwanegu'r ffwythiant hwn fel galwad yn ôl yr hidlydd, gan ddefnyddio galwad WordPress <em>add_filter</em>. Ac yn olaf, mewnosodwch ef yn ffeil functions.php eich thema neu ffeil eich ategyn eich hun."

